WEBVTT

01:43.210 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.170 --> 01:49.070
[Episode 10]

01:49.520 --> 01:50.509
Nice shots,

01:52.400 --> 01:53.110
Wang Qiang.

01:58.560 --> 01:59.370
Wang Qiang!

02:00.910 --> 02:01.390
Stop there!

02:01.410 --> 02:02.000
Stop there!

02:05.810 --> 02:06.530
Stop there!

02:13.850 --> 02:14.470
Don't move!

02:15.090 --> 02:15.630
Get down!

02:15.630 --> 02:16.120
Let go of me!

02:16.160 --> 02:17.150
-Get down!
-Let go of me!

02:17.570 --> 02:18.160
Don't move!

02:19.670 --> 02:20.280
Don't move!

02:27.100 --> 02:28.070
Handcuff him and take him to the car.

02:28.670 --> 02:29.390
Don't move!

02:37.210 --> 02:38.590
Sure enough, at this critical moment,

02:38.630 --> 02:40.390
it has to be Professor Yu who steps in.

02:41.150 --> 02:42.690
How did you know it was him?

02:43.550 --> 02:45.070
When I was touching up my makeup earlier,

02:45.110 --> 02:46.270
I observed everyone.

02:46.700 --> 02:47.670
What if he wasn't even

02:47.670 --> 02:49.260
in this cafe?

02:49.920 --> 02:51.440
That's possible too.

02:52.340 --> 02:53.150
But

02:53.190 --> 02:54.630
when I walked into the cafe,

02:54.650 --> 02:56.030
everyone looked at me

02:56.150 --> 02:57.240
except for him.

03:11.560 --> 03:12.340
Alright.

03:12.370 --> 03:13.170
You have a way with it.

03:14.510 --> 03:15.930
Humans are visual animals,

03:15.950 --> 03:17.180
especially men.

03:17.510 --> 03:19.950
Men are more likely to choose younger,

03:20.110 --> 03:20.770
healthy,

03:20.970 --> 03:22.810
and energetic individuals as partners.

03:24.030 --> 03:25.350
So men are more easily attracted to

03:25.430 --> 03:27.460
beautiful and sexy appearances.

03:27.750 --> 03:28.840
This is the nature of men.

03:31.390 --> 03:32.150
Got it.

03:33.710 --> 03:34.780
But this time,

03:35.150 --> 03:36.150
really,

03:36.870 --> 03:37.630
thank you so much

03:37.750 --> 03:38.590
for helping us.

03:43.740 --> 03:44.670
Professor Yu.

03:46.600 --> 03:47.780
Captain Jiang.

03:47.810 --> 03:48.740
What brings you here?

03:48.829 --> 03:49.920
Not busy, huh?

03:51.000 --> 03:51.960
The class just ended.

03:53.010 --> 03:53.780
Is something wrong?

03:53.890 --> 03:55.820
Yes, I have a small favor to ask.

03:56.510 --> 03:57.490
What is it?

03:59.560 --> 04:01.280
What do you mean by "us"?

04:01.300 --> 04:03.190
I'm just helping you, Jiang Chengyi.

04:04.840 --> 04:06.530
Here you go again.

04:08.310 --> 04:09.000
Forget it.

04:09.020 --> 04:09.870
I was just kidding.

04:10.670 --> 04:12.110
I just wanted to see

04:12.270 --> 04:13.400
if you're still thinking about

04:13.400 --> 04:14.740
your ex-girlfriend.

04:18.300 --> 04:20.269
I'll go take the guy back first.

04:20.350 --> 04:21.529
Let's grab a meal sometime.

04:21.829 --> 04:23.070
I don't have time to eat with you.

04:23.420 --> 04:24.590
But if you have any psychological issues,

04:24.590 --> 04:25.470
you can reach out to me.

04:26.950 --> 04:27.720
Thanks.

04:27.750 --> 04:28.750
Bye bye. See you.

04:34.830 --> 04:35.470
Sir,

04:35.950 --> 04:36.830
what have I done

04:36.830 --> 04:37.740
to get arrested?

04:41.630 --> 04:42.630
You're not admitting it, huh?

04:44.190 --> 04:44.830
Admit what?

04:44.870 --> 04:45.390
See for yourself.

04:50.770 --> 04:51.940
It's too dark to see clearly.

04:53.040 --> 04:53.940
Can't see clearly?

04:55.790 --> 04:56.940
Here, look at this.

05:03.630 --> 05:04.470
I can't even see the face...

05:04.490 --> 05:05.770
Look carefully before you say that!

05:09.590 --> 05:10.470
I can't even see the face clearly.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.710
How could it be me?

05:13.510 --> 05:14.030
What about this one?

05:14.600 --> 05:15.830
This is the one you bought, right?

05:24.270 --> 05:25.010
Wang Qiang,

05:27.480 --> 05:29.050
why did you follow that girl?

05:33.850 --> 05:35.000
Which girl?

05:35.640 --> 05:36.900
I don't understand what you're saying.

05:39.480 --> 05:41.159
I'm talking to you properly now.

05:41.590 --> 05:43.080
You'd better tell me everything you can.

05:43.760 --> 05:45.280
Why were you following the girl

05:45.310 --> 05:46.310
in the photo on your phone?

05:48.600 --> 05:49.730
Was anyone directing you?

05:51.670 --> 05:52.650
No one directed me.

05:53.500 --> 05:54.280
I've never done

05:54.310 --> 05:55.190
anything you're talking about.

05:58.220 --> 06:00.000
We found a large amount of evidence

06:00.750 --> 06:01.910
on your computer and phone.

06:02.820 --> 06:04.710
There are numerous photos of women you've secretly taken,

06:05.270 --> 06:06.350
records of trafficking,

06:07.840 --> 06:09.040
and banned drugs

06:09.070 --> 06:10.070
you've purchased.

06:11.390 --> 06:12.390
How many years do you want to be sentenced to?

06:15.420 --> 06:16.750
Let me ask you again.

06:17.710 --> 06:18.420
Why were you

06:18.750 --> 06:20.030
following that female doctor?

06:24.190 --> 06:25.660
When I see attractive girls,

06:26.230 --> 06:27.640
I'd casually take their photos,

06:27.680 --> 06:29.080
then edit their faces

06:29.580 --> 06:30.550
onto explicit images

06:31.720 --> 06:32.330
and

06:33.350 --> 06:34.470
sell them online for money.

06:34.920 --> 06:35.670
That day,

06:36.450 --> 06:38.210
I happened to run into that female doctor.

06:38.230 --> 06:39.600
I thought she looked good,

06:40.780 --> 06:42.140
so I casually took a few photos of her.

06:43.310 --> 06:43.990
But I haven't had the chance

06:43.990 --> 06:45.110
to edit the photos yet.

06:45.420 --> 06:46.530
They're still on my phone.

06:46.550 --> 06:47.390
You can check them if you want,

06:47.390 --> 06:48.040
sir.

06:48.320 --> 06:49.010
I saw them.

06:50.320 --> 06:51.550
So you were the one

06:51.550 --> 06:52.390
in the alley that day.

06:53.590 --> 06:54.110
Right?

06:56.670 --> 06:57.880
What were you planning to do that day?

07:00.340 --> 07:01.290
I saw that

07:02.230 --> 07:03.390
no one was in the alley,

07:05.190 --> 07:07.130
so I... I just wanted to…

07:08.670 --> 07:09.510
take advantage of her.

07:12.400 --> 07:13.430
Do you know her?

07:14.590 --> 07:15.610
I don't know her.

07:16.200 --> 07:17.200
I take so many photos every day.

07:17.230 --> 07:18.280
How would I know who she is?

07:18.370 --> 07:19.250
You don't know her.

07:19.910 --> 07:21.190
Why did you repeatedly follow her?

07:21.210 --> 07:23.100
I just thought she was attractive.

07:31.880 --> 07:34.750
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

07:34.670 --> 07:35.270
Yan.

07:35.270 --> 07:36.610
This place is crowded.

07:37.440 --> 07:39.400
I don't want to eat at the cafeteria.

07:40.500 --> 07:41.350
Wen.

07:41.430 --> 07:42.490
What brings you here?

07:43.120 --> 07:43.870
I came to bring you

07:43.870 --> 07:44.550
movie tickets.

07:47.440 --> 07:48.600
What movie?

07:49.190 --> 07:50.540
It's a movie produced by our company.

07:50.590 --> 07:51.590
Tomorrow at 7:30 PM.

07:51.790 --> 07:52.670
I'd like to have my friends over

07:52.790 --> 07:53.670
to watch and critique the movie.

07:54.690 --> 07:56.310
Wasn't this movie

07:56.350 --> 07:57.970
awarded at a film festival before?

07:58.710 --> 08:00.500
It was just a small award.

08:00.710 --> 08:02.040
You're being too modest.

08:02.390 --> 08:04.170
Will Feng be coming?

08:05.700 --> 08:07.630
He's filming, so he probably can't make it.

08:08.480 --> 08:09.340
Okay.

08:11.010 --> 08:12.640
What do you think? Are you free?

08:13.100 --> 08:15.480
Tomorrow, we're on the day shift,

08:15.910 --> 08:17.060
so we should be able to go.

08:17.560 --> 08:18.100
Great, then.

08:18.230 --> 08:19.940
I'd like to thank you in advance

08:20.190 --> 08:21.040
for coming.

08:22.350 --> 08:23.070
I'll ask the driver

08:23.070 --> 08:23.550
to pick you up tomorrow.

08:23.590 --> 08:24.230
No need.

08:24.310 --> 08:25.510
We'll just take the subway.

08:26.270 --> 08:26.790
The subway?

08:28.190 --> 08:29.070
Has the person been caught?

08:31.300 --> 08:32.340
I believe

08:32.370 --> 08:33.669
Captain Jiang will catch him.

08:35.240 --> 08:36.110
Are you two

08:36.110 --> 08:37.500
rekindling your love?

08:37.950 --> 08:38.669
Nonsense.

08:40.280 --> 08:40.720
Alright.

08:41.030 --> 08:41.780
See you tomorrow.

08:43.159 --> 08:43.909
Thank you.

08:43.929 --> 08:44.580
You're welcome.

08:45.030 --> 08:45.860
Bye bye.

09:00.390 --> 09:01.190
Why don't you

09:01.920 --> 09:03.470
ask Captain Jiang

09:03.490 --> 09:04.430
to go with you?

09:07.970 --> 09:09.340
To the premiere.

09:08.620 --> 09:10.270
["Half Love"]

09:11.590 --> 09:12.590
Anyway,

09:12.670 --> 09:14.140
you are

09:14.550 --> 09:15.990
into him now,

09:16.220 --> 09:16.950
aren't you?

09:17.410 --> 09:19.190
What nonsense is that?

09:19.510 --> 09:20.430
It's a great opportunity for you

09:20.450 --> 09:21.510
to watch a movie together.

09:23.000 --> 09:23.960
Don't you want to watch it?

09:23.990 --> 09:24.510
Didn't we agree

09:24.510 --> 09:25.790
to watch it together?

09:26.590 --> 09:27.870
But Feng isn't involved in this.

09:27.870 --> 09:28.710
Why should I go?

09:29.000 --> 09:30.360
I'm a true fan.

09:30.710 --> 09:33.580
If I go to see other handsome guys,

09:33.910 --> 09:35.470
I'll feel guilty.

09:35.620 --> 09:37.140
I'll hit you. Believe it or not.

09:37.160 --> 09:38.230
Can't you watch with me?

09:38.270 --> 09:39.530
You've gone crazy chasing stars.

09:39.950 --> 09:40.690
I'm not!

09:42.370 --> 09:42.950
I want to eat this.

09:42.990 --> 09:43.860
You can have all of it.

09:44.230 --> 09:46.620
It is indeed unrequited love on my part.

09:46.730 --> 09:47.510
But...

09:48.690 --> 09:50.390
But you're different from me.

09:50.750 --> 09:52.330
Mutual affection—

09:52.410 --> 09:53.640
how rare it is.

09:54.790 --> 09:56.150
You should cherish it

09:56.470 --> 09:59.030
and create more chances to be alone together.

09:59.070 --> 09:59.750
Got it?

10:01.360 --> 10:02.080
No.

10:02.110 --> 10:02.840
The thing is...

10:04.250 --> 10:05.390
I don't know

10:06.380 --> 10:08.240
how the other person feels about me.

10:08.350 --> 10:09.110
So,

10:09.140 --> 10:10.620
that's even more reason to go watch the movie.

10:10.930 --> 10:11.910
Watching a movie

10:11.950 --> 10:13.260
is basically a date.

10:13.770 --> 10:16.530
If he agrees to go with you,

10:16.650 --> 10:17.720
what does it mean?

10:18.720 --> 10:20.510
It means

10:20.540 --> 10:22.900
he still has feelings for you.

10:26.630 --> 10:27.800
But you see,

10:28.350 --> 10:29.440
we've just

10:30.450 --> 10:32.550
started reconnecting,

10:32.750 --> 10:33.990
isn't going to watch the movie

10:34.010 --> 10:35.010
too fast

10:35.720 --> 10:36.920
of a step?

10:37.180 --> 10:38.010
What's wrong?

10:38.440 --> 10:39.400
Didn't you watch movies

10:39.430 --> 10:40.560
when you were together?

10:42.870 --> 10:43.920
Really.

10:45.330 --> 10:46.630
Yan, I'm telling you,

10:47.630 --> 10:48.940
both our profession

10:49.080 --> 10:50.410
and his

10:50.550 --> 10:51.850
are very unique.

10:51.870 --> 10:53.040
You know that, right?

10:53.360 --> 10:54.860
You're a doctor,

10:54.990 --> 10:56.430
and he's a police officer.

10:56.960 --> 10:58.070
At every moment,

10:58.150 --> 10:59.750
we face numerous dangers

10:59.910 --> 11:01.430
and the threat of death.

11:01.770 --> 11:03.380
We never know which will come first:

11:03.540 --> 11:06.130
our tomorrow, or our end.

11:06.290 --> 11:07.140
So,

11:07.550 --> 11:08.550
when you get the chance

11:08.630 --> 11:10.150
to grasp happiness,

11:10.350 --> 11:12.700
make sure you hold on to it tightly.

11:13.070 --> 11:14.960
Hold on tightly, do you understand?

11:15.470 --> 11:16.970
No matter

11:17.030 --> 11:18.300
what the result is,

11:18.550 --> 11:19.780
but

11:19.990 --> 11:21.250
at least

11:21.760 --> 11:22.590
if you've tried,

11:23.570 --> 11:24.780
you won't have any regrets.

11:26.550 --> 11:27.360
Right?

11:35.650 --> 11:39.100
["Half Love"]

11:36.030 --> 11:37.220
Go.

11:42.180 --> 11:42.950
Senior.

11:43.240 --> 11:44.750
As for the photos taken by Wang Qiang,

11:44.830 --> 11:46.070
the ones on his phone and computer,

11:46.110 --> 11:47.270
I went through them, and there are over ten thousand.

11:47.290 --> 11:48.430
I estimate he's photographed

11:48.430 --> 11:49.350
more than a thousand girls.

11:49.950 --> 11:50.840
So disgusting.

11:51.910 --> 11:52.570
Yeah.

11:52.830 --> 11:54.500
Wang Qiang especially likes to take pictures

11:54.590 --> 11:55.310
of people on buses

11:55.350 --> 11:56.660
or subways.

11:59.070 --> 11:59.600
Senior,

12:00.120 --> 12:01.030
though Wang Qiang

12:01.070 --> 12:02.230
is quite a troublemaker,

12:02.550 --> 12:03.980
I think he's telling the truth

12:04.010 --> 12:05.340
in this case.

12:05.630 --> 12:06.790
He definitely didn't know

12:06.790 --> 12:07.590
Dr. Lu before.

12:07.990 --> 12:08.670
Don't worry.

12:10.940 --> 12:11.900
Transfer him to the detention center.

12:12.170 --> 12:12.550
Okay.

12:12.720 --> 12:13.290
Alright.

12:17.590 --> 12:18.340
Yue.

12:18.470 --> 12:25.170
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

12:19.030 --> 12:19.790
Smell this bread.

12:19.790 --> 12:20.750
Do you think it's gone bad?

12:20.830 --> 12:22.270
Smell my shoes. Do they stink?

12:30.570 --> 12:31.990
If it wasn't Wang Qiang,

12:33.020 --> 12:34.210
then who else could be

12:34.230 --> 12:35.420
pretending to be Deng Man?

12:41.590 --> 12:44.150
[Huiting Complex]

12:48.520 --> 12:49.240
["Half Love"]

13:15.200 --> 13:15.630
Hello,

13:15.630 --> 13:16.710
the subscriber you dialed

13:16.750 --> 13:17.960
is busy now.

13:17.990 --> 13:19.550
Please try again later.

13:33.210 --> 13:33.800
Hello?

13:35.920 --> 13:36.860
Why can't I

13:37.110 --> 13:38.330
get through to your phone?

13:38.910 --> 13:39.630
I...

13:40.270 --> 13:42.080
I've been calling you,

13:42.110 --> 13:43.700
but it seems the line is busy.

13:44.030 --> 13:45.070
Yes, I've been trying to call you too.

13:46.270 --> 13:47.300
Well...

13:47.470 --> 13:48.350
Why are you calling me?

13:51.310 --> 13:52.310
I...

13:55.070 --> 13:57.630
I just wanted to ask,

13:57.950 --> 13:59.560
did you catch that bad guy

13:59.590 --> 14:00.790
from last time?

14:00.910 --> 14:02.350
Weren't you in a hurry to leave?

14:02.830 --> 14:03.440
The person's been caught.

14:03.500 --> 14:04.070
Don't worry.

14:05.240 --> 14:06.190
That's good.

14:07.190 --> 14:08.230
So is that person

14:08.310 --> 14:09.910
the one pretending to be Deng Man?

14:10.390 --> 14:11.350
It's not him.

14:12.050 --> 14:13.460
I'll keep looking into this.

14:16.590 --> 14:17.110
No worries.

14:17.750 --> 14:18.580
Thanks.

14:24.390 --> 14:25.030
Hello?

14:25.860 --> 14:26.650
Are you...

14:26.870 --> 14:28.270
Are you still there?

14:30.240 --> 14:31.630
I'm still at the bureau.

14:34.230 --> 14:35.770
Are you busy

14:36.310 --> 14:37.800
tomorrow as well?

14:38.550 --> 14:39.780
Do you have anything

14:39.970 --> 14:41.030
planned for tomorrow?

14:42.870 --> 14:44.990
No big deal.

14:45.020 --> 14:46.790
If you're too busy, it's fine.

14:46.850 --> 14:47.820
I'm free.

14:48.530 --> 14:49.870
Let's have dinner together tomorrow night.

14:52.200 --> 14:53.080
Here's the thing.

14:53.110 --> 14:54.830
Wen gave me two tickets

14:55.650 --> 14:58.010
for the movie premiere.

14:58.350 --> 14:59.500
And

14:59.710 --> 15:00.990
tomorrow at 7 p.m.,

15:01.030 --> 15:02.310
I was wondering if you...

15:02.330 --> 15:03.080
No problem.

15:03.200 --> 15:04.820
Send me the time and location,

15:05.490 --> 15:06.400
I'll go with you.

15:09.310 --> 15:09.990
That's it.

15:10.510 --> 15:11.030
Alright.

15:11.130 --> 15:11.750
Okay.

15:32.040 --> 15:32.700
Good morning.

15:36.110 --> 15:36.920
Good morning.

15:41.900 --> 15:43.300
You need to fix this.

15:43.750 --> 15:44.620
You have these

15:44.920 --> 15:45.750
dark circles.

15:45.830 --> 15:46.150
Come on.

15:46.170 --> 15:46.870
Lift it up.

15:48.460 --> 15:50.160
Enough, I was born with them.

15:50.340 --> 15:51.190
You need to cover them up.

15:51.210 --> 15:51.780
Okay.

15:52.610 --> 15:54.100
What are you wearing today?

15:54.240 --> 15:56.590
I'm just wearing what I came in.

15:56.710 --> 15:57.630
What you came in?

15:58.510 --> 15:59.310
That won't do.

15:59.330 --> 15:59.910
You...

15:59.990 --> 16:00.680
You'd better hurry

16:00.710 --> 16:01.590
and go buy a dress.

16:01.830 --> 16:02.830
Do I have to buy a dress?

16:02.910 --> 16:03.590
Of course.

16:03.630 --> 16:04.550
You can't go to the movie date

16:04.570 --> 16:06.030
without a dress.

16:06.110 --> 16:06.950
You need to look good,

16:06.970 --> 16:07.580
okay?

16:07.990 --> 16:08.790
Yan.

16:08.990 --> 16:10.270
You're actually putting on makeup?

16:12.480 --> 16:14.100
This makeup looks like

16:14.150 --> 16:15.350
you're not wearing any at all.

16:15.370 --> 16:16.310
Dr. Huang,

16:16.830 --> 16:18.390
do you know that,

16:18.580 --> 16:20.510
as a guy,

16:20.860 --> 16:21.980
having high EQ

16:22.130 --> 16:23.420
makes it easier

16:23.440 --> 16:24.640
to win a girl's affection?

16:25.370 --> 16:26.760
Don't touch my stuff.

16:27.030 --> 16:28.260
Such a big setup,

16:28.390 --> 16:29.350
are you going on a date?

16:29.390 --> 16:30.400
Of course.

16:30.670 --> 16:31.630
You think it's for you?

16:31.680 --> 16:32.560
Don't tell him,

16:32.600 --> 16:33.280
or everyone in the hospital

16:33.310 --> 16:34.270
will know by tomorrow.

16:34.290 --> 16:35.020
You're right.

16:35.400 --> 16:36.430
That's for sure.

16:36.460 --> 16:37.380
Since I saw this,

16:37.400 --> 16:38.580
I have to tell everyone.

16:38.600 --> 16:39.360
I've got to live up

16:39.380 --> 16:40.610
to my reputation as the king of gossip.

16:40.790 --> 16:41.690
My goodness.

16:41.750 --> 16:43.400
I'm speechless.

16:44.350 --> 16:45.350
Do you know

16:45.440 --> 16:47.250
why Matron Qiao

16:47.270 --> 16:48.710
always ignores you?

16:49.350 --> 16:49.990
Why?

16:50.310 --> 16:51.230
Because

16:51.390 --> 16:52.300
you talk too much!

16:53.670 --> 16:54.870
Talk too much?

16:55.510 --> 16:56.240
Lipstick.

16:56.630 --> 16:57.380
Do I?

17:01.120 --> 17:01.900
Purse your lips.

17:03.410 --> 17:04.160
Take a look.

17:05.130 --> 17:05.760
Not bad.

17:05.790 --> 17:06.609
I think it looks good.

17:06.740 --> 17:07.540
It's quite natural.

17:07.630 --> 17:08.230
What do you think?

17:08.250 --> 17:08.819
Is it too red?

17:09.200 --> 17:11.599
I personally think it's a bit too red.

17:11.869 --> 17:12.550
The eye makeup

17:12.550 --> 17:13.630
could be more intense.

17:14.150 --> 17:16.270
As for the blush, it's actually unnecessary...

17:16.300 --> 17:17.109
Why are you asking him?

17:17.109 --> 17:17.750
He knows nothing.

17:17.780 --> 17:18.800
Hurry up.

17:18.829 --> 17:20.030
You still need to buy a dress.

17:20.030 --> 17:20.390
Oh yeah.

17:20.430 --> 17:21.540
I'll head out first.

17:22.800 --> 17:23.810
Good luck, Yan!

17:24.230 --> 17:25.589
Buy a nicer dress.

17:25.609 --> 17:25.960
Alright.

17:42.070 --> 17:44.730
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

17:45.490 --> 17:48.520
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

17:49.670 --> 17:52.060
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

17:52.680 --> 17:55.270
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

17:57.010 --> 17:59.760
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

18:00.370 --> 18:02.880
♫What we lack is not just time♫

18:04.750 --> 18:07.220
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

18:07.950 --> 18:10.460
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

18:11.170 --> 18:14.000
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

18:14.920 --> 18:17.690
♫Romance only exists with you♫

18:18.590 --> 18:20.730
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

18:21.520 --> 18:25.190
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

18:26.100 --> 18:28.640
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

18:27.390 --> 18:28.150
Hello.

18:28.170 --> 18:29.320
Is there anything you'd like to see?

18:29.350 --> 18:31.020
Do you have any recommendations?

18:29.840 --> 18:32.210
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

18:33.010 --> 18:35.400
♫Endless loving and longing♫

18:33.250 --> 18:34.270
These are all new arrivals.

18:34.350 --> 18:35.350
But I think this dress

18:35.370 --> 18:36.490
suits you perfectly.

18:36.580 --> 18:43.550
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

18:37.480 --> 18:38.490
This one?

18:40.250 --> 18:41.070
Would you like to try it on?

18:41.110 --> 18:41.750
Can I try it?

18:41.770 --> 18:42.410
Of course.

18:42.540 --> 18:43.070
Okay.

18:43.070 --> 18:43.800
The fitting room is over here.

18:43.850 --> 18:44.270
Thank you.

18:44.290 --> 18:45.280
I'll get you a new one.

18:49.910 --> 18:51.120
The mirror is over here.

18:56.610 --> 18:59.260
♫Holding hands while heading to the best outcome♫

18:57.370 --> 18:58.170
Well...

19:00.320 --> 19:03.290
♫Learning the beauty of waiting♫

19:01.560 --> 19:03.020
I feel like

19:03.430 --> 19:04.710
it's a bit too tight.

19:04.430 --> 19:06.860
♫You know me best, I don't need to speak a word♫

19:04.740 --> 19:05.430
I'm not really...

19:06.110 --> 19:06.590
I can't put it into words.

19:06.710 --> 19:08.330
It fits really well.

19:07.820 --> 19:10.410
♫A special thing only you know it♫

19:08.370 --> 19:09.240
This piece

19:09.270 --> 19:10.390
is part of our Winter Love Song collection,

19:10.410 --> 19:11.350
specially designed for girls

19:11.430 --> 19:12.750
to wear on dates.

19:11.950 --> 19:14.710
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

19:13.390 --> 19:14.750
I think you look great in it.

19:14.910 --> 19:15.910
And for dates,

19:15.410 --> 19:18.070
♫I'll engrave every fluttering moment♫

19:15.950 --> 19:16.750
we should

19:16.790 --> 19:17.710
dress up beautifully.

19:17.730 --> 19:19.010
Are you going on a date?

19:19.290 --> 19:19.930
No.

19:19.380 --> 19:21.880
♫I kiss your forehead, as starlight watches us grow old together♫

19:21.490 --> 19:22.860
Well, kind of.

19:22.780 --> 19:25.270
♫I want to hear you say you don't regret♫

19:25.940 --> 19:28.610
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

19:26.230 --> 19:26.910
That's perfect then.

19:26.990 --> 19:28.030
In SC,

19:28.030 --> 19:29.740
we also have a matching fragrance from the same collection.

19:29.990 --> 19:32.430
♫Romance only exists with you♫

19:30.150 --> 19:31.600
It's also designed for dates.

19:31.710 --> 19:32.510
Would you like to try it?

19:32.630 --> 19:33.520
No.

19:33.500 --> 19:35.330
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

19:33.660 --> 19:34.880
Actually, about the dress,

19:34.910 --> 19:37.150
do you have another style?

19:36.350 --> 19:40.080
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

19:37.270 --> 19:38.930
I don't feel comfortable wearing it.

19:39.060 --> 19:39.940
This one then.

19:40.070 --> 19:40.900
It looks nice.

19:40.920 --> 19:43.610
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

19:42.190 --> 19:42.610
You...

19:42.830 --> 19:44.170
Why are you here?

19:44.480 --> 19:45.280
I was just passing by

19:44.640 --> 19:47.230
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

19:45.350 --> 19:46.080
and happened to see you.

19:47.590 --> 19:48.510
Do you think

19:48.080 --> 19:50.300
♫Endless loving and longing♫

19:49.430 --> 19:50.310
it's okay?

19:50.460 --> 19:51.430
It looks really good.

19:51.520 --> 19:58.600
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

19:52.860 --> 19:53.570
Alright then,

19:53.630 --> 19:55.230
I'll go pay now.

19:55.550 --> 19:56.790
Okay, this way please.

20:01.120 --> 20:01.890
I've already paid.

20:01.920 --> 20:02.570
Let's go.

20:03.630 --> 20:04.570
You bought it?

20:04.670 --> 20:06.160
Yeah, it's so beautiful.

20:08.640 --> 20:09.440
Thank you.

20:11.430 --> 20:11.900
Let's go.

20:12.100 --> 20:13.000
We still have a date to go to.

20:18.850 --> 20:20.680
May I ask Director Jiang

20:20.710 --> 20:21.710
what your thoughts and reflections

20:21.790 --> 20:22.720
are on this film?

20:22.360 --> 20:25.920
["Half Love"]

20:23.190 --> 20:24.230
Our movie

20:24.360 --> 20:25.150
is about love.

20:25.180 --> 20:25.720
Mr. Wen.

20:26.290 --> 20:27.220
I personally think

20:27.270 --> 20:28.020
love

20:28.150 --> 20:30.120
is adapted from real-life experiences.

20:30.310 --> 20:30.880
Forget it,

20:30.920 --> 20:31.960
I won't spoil it.

20:34.100 --> 20:34.880
Hi there.

20:42.510 --> 20:43.290
Captain Jiang.

20:45.550 --> 20:46.810
Why isn't Qianqian here?

20:47.350 --> 20:48.310
Something came up.

20:48.350 --> 20:49.470
She said she couldn't make it.

20:49.790 --> 20:50.160
That's right.

20:50.190 --> 20:51.270
I'm here to keep her company.

20:52.790 --> 20:54.160
Captain Jiang's vacation

20:54.190 --> 20:55.350
is unusually long this time.

20:57.040 --> 20:57.770
Yeah.

21:00.140 --> 21:01.650
Well, let's get together more often.

21:02.070 --> 21:03.310
Sure, depends on the schedule.

21:05.550 --> 21:06.510
The movie is about to start.

21:06.530 --> 21:07.530
Shall we go in first?

21:08.250 --> 21:08.880
Let's go.

21:16.350 --> 21:17.690
Row 3.

21:17.750 --> 21:18.700
Seats 15 and 16.

21:23.110 --> 21:23.840
Be careful.

21:39.850 --> 21:40.500
Mr. Wen.

21:41.040 --> 21:41.870
Long time no see.

21:41.900 --> 21:42.790
Long time no see.

21:42.830 --> 21:43.550
Come on, take a seat.

21:43.550 --> 21:43.910
Okay.

21:45.690 --> 21:46.580
I apologize for the lack of hospitality.

21:47.840 --> 21:48.360
Mr. Wen.

21:48.390 --> 21:48.910
Hello, Director.

21:48.930 --> 21:49.670
We're all waiting for you.

21:49.690 --> 21:50.070
Here.

21:50.090 --> 21:50.470
Have a seat.

21:50.470 --> 21:50.950
Director, have a seat.

22:01.090 --> 22:01.810
Mr. Wen,

22:01.850 --> 22:02.850
shall we start now?

22:04.430 --> 22:04.910
Yes.

22:37.140 --> 22:41.910
[Performing with a mask on]

23:34.780 --> 23:35.870
Enjoy the movie

23:35.890 --> 23:36.790
with Officer.

23:36.880 --> 23:38.150
Hope things progress quickly

23:38.230 --> 23:39.200
for you both tonight.

24:53.730 --> 24:56.650
[My promise, waiting to be spoken]

25:13.450 --> 25:14.270
Dad.

25:16.290 --> 25:16.930
Dad.

25:18.630 --> 25:19.230
You're back.

25:20.510 --> 25:22.080
I got the exchange spot.

25:22.760 --> 25:24.800
Get me a glass of water.

25:30.930 --> 25:31.740
Dad, water.

25:40.480 --> 25:42.210
You know it's hot, and you still pour it for me to drink?

25:42.230 --> 25:43.740
You're trying to burn me, aren't you?

25:44.670 --> 25:45.760
You blockhead.

25:47.910 --> 25:49.510
What did you just say to me?

25:49.750 --> 25:50.710
What are you going to do?

25:51.900 --> 25:52.550
I...

25:53.540 --> 25:54.130
I...

25:54.590 --> 25:55.990
I got the exchange spot.

25:56.560 --> 25:58.130
I can go study abroad now.

25:58.580 --> 26:00.770
You, study abroad?

26:01.990 --> 26:03.610
You're just like your mom, a real handful.

26:07.360 --> 26:09.230
My mom has always been good to you.

26:09.500 --> 26:10.600
Has your mom been good to me?

26:11.970 --> 26:13.550
Hasn't your mom been good to you too?

26:14.720 --> 26:15.500
She's good to you,

26:15.530 --> 26:16.730
so why doesn't she want you anymore?

26:16.760 --> 26:17.790
She's good to you,

26:17.810 --> 26:19.560
so why did she leave with someone else?

26:19.590 --> 26:20.850
Remember,

26:21.070 --> 26:21.950
I've been taking care of you

26:22.020 --> 26:23.390
since you were little

26:23.430 --> 26:24.750
and have raised you to this point.

26:24.790 --> 26:25.950
I put you through college,

26:25.970 --> 26:27.450
and now you want to leave me?

26:27.510 --> 26:28.800
Listen.

26:29.190 --> 26:30.700
You're not going anywhere.

26:30.790 --> 26:32.640
If one day I don't want to live anymore,

26:32.710 --> 26:34.440
you'll have to die with me!

26:34.470 --> 26:35.430
Do you understand?

26:35.510 --> 26:37.130
Get lost!

27:01.440 --> 27:09.240
[Dangerous Water Depth, No Swimming]

27:24.010 --> 27:26.270
[Dangerous Water Depth, No Swimming]

27:36.850 --> 27:37.820
[Dangerous Water Depth, No Swimming]

27:37.180 --> 27:38.550
What are you doing?

27:40.770 --> 27:41.640
Wen.

27:43.110 --> 27:44.750
The sign over there says:

27:44.750 --> 27:46.440
"Dangerous Water Depth."

27:57.670 --> 27:58.380
You...

27:59.280 --> 28:00.730
What's wrong with you?

28:07.810 --> 28:09.380
Can you hold my umbrella?

28:14.810 --> 28:16.110
I'll perform something for you.

28:16.150 --> 28:16.990
Hold this for me.

28:22.890 --> 28:24.170
Do you know how to skip stones?

28:25.640 --> 28:26.740
Let me show you.

28:27.180 --> 28:29.960
[Dangerous Water Depth, No Swimming]

28:30.910 --> 28:32.160
I'm not good at it either,

28:32.830 --> 28:33.790
but I just managed to hit two skips.

28:33.810 --> 28:34.810
Did you see that?

28:41.260 --> 28:42.910
Let me share

28:42.930 --> 28:44.290
a little story with you.

28:46.040 --> 28:47.920
Actually, I've been pretty dumb

28:48.040 --> 28:48.960
all my life.

28:49.340 --> 28:51.040
Like, really dumb.

28:52.090 --> 28:53.670
How dumb was I?

28:54.390 --> 28:55.640
Well,

28:55.750 --> 28:56.630
I couldn't even memorize

28:56.650 --> 28:57.550
the multiplication table.

28:57.580 --> 28:58.710
My mom was so angry

28:58.740 --> 28:59.710
that she chased me around to hit me.

28:59.740 --> 29:00.870
But it didn't work.

29:00.900 --> 29:01.970
I was still that dumb.

29:02.220 --> 29:03.190
But later,

29:03.270 --> 29:05.640
I learned a saying:

29:05.990 --> 29:07.390
"A slow sparrow should make an early start."

29:07.750 --> 29:09.570
I was willing to be that slow sparrow,

29:09.720 --> 29:11.030
so I studied quietly and in secret.

29:11.230 --> 29:12.120
And in the end,

29:12.270 --> 29:13.420
I was the one

29:13.480 --> 29:15.690
who got into Ninghai University.

29:15.910 --> 29:17.310
I was so proud of myself.

29:17.390 --> 29:19.440
But then, when I came to this school,

29:20.150 --> 29:21.390
I found out that everyone around me

29:21.410 --> 29:22.640
was better than me.

29:22.710 --> 29:24.430
There were academic stars everywhere,

29:24.640 --> 29:25.750
just like you.

29:25.830 --> 29:26.990
Do you know what they call you

29:27.030 --> 29:27.910
in our class?

29:28.110 --> 29:29.830
They call you a genius.

29:29.890 --> 29:32.070
Even Teacher Han is totally smitten by you.

29:32.390 --> 29:34.790
He praises you every day at school—

29:34.810 --> 29:35.930
both in class

29:36.000 --> 29:36.950
and outside of class.

29:37.020 --> 29:37.710
Your exercise book

29:37.750 --> 29:39.350
has even been circulated among our batch.

29:40.540 --> 29:41.750
I might not be as amazing

29:41.750 --> 29:42.430
as you think.

29:43.910 --> 29:44.840
You're being modest.

29:44.880 --> 29:45.990
I know,

29:46.020 --> 29:47.600
smart people like you,

29:47.670 --> 29:48.990
born to be excellent,

29:49.020 --> 29:49.970
are just like that.

29:50.110 --> 29:51.000
You can't even see

29:51.030 --> 29:52.110
how great the shine is

29:52.130 --> 29:53.450
within you.

30:02.920 --> 30:04.440
Are you feeling a bit happier now?

30:07.770 --> 30:08.370
Look,

30:08.390 --> 30:09.030
I'm so dumb,

30:09.060 --> 30:10.460
but I still live happily.

30:13.680 --> 30:15.540
Don't be upset, okay?

30:16.390 --> 30:17.640
Let me secretly tell you

30:17.670 --> 30:18.470
a little secret.

30:19.790 --> 30:20.980
Actually,

30:21.310 --> 30:22.760
a lot of people see you

30:22.870 --> 30:25.160
as their target to catch up with.

30:26.250 --> 30:27.720
Feeling a bit happier now?

30:29.750 --> 30:30.690
Wen,

30:31.000 --> 30:32.370
you're amazing.

30:38.110 --> 30:39.350
Don't be unhappy.

30:43.710 --> 30:45.440
I'm off to evening self-study now.

30:45.550 --> 30:46.620
See you.

30:51.900 --> 30:53.150
Your umbrella!

30:53.810 --> 30:55.100
It's yours now.

31:36.370 --> 31:40.690
[Silence]

33:09.220 --> 33:09.830
Yan.

33:11.970 --> 33:12.640
Wen.

33:12.740 --> 33:13.610
What are you thinking about?

33:15.830 --> 33:16.790
Nothing much.

33:17.020 --> 33:17.910
Just...

33:18.590 --> 33:20.410
Zoning out, throwing little stones.

33:27.020 --> 33:28.740
Do you like lakes?

33:31.830 --> 33:33.790
I feel that looking at a lake

33:34.990 --> 33:36.830
can make the heart very peaceful.

33:42.110 --> 33:43.310
I really want to visit

33:43.350 --> 33:44.750
Lake Baikal.

33:45.350 --> 33:47.320
I've heard it's called

33:47.430 --> 33:48.790
the "Pearl of Siberia."

33:50.950 --> 33:52.390
Coincidentally, Teacher Han and I

33:52.430 --> 33:54.820
are going to Russia for an academic conference

33:54.950 --> 33:55.790
this weekend.

33:56.040 --> 33:57.370
If I have time,

33:57.410 --> 33:58.900
I can go take a look at it for you.

33:59.450 --> 34:00.380
Really?

34:00.830 --> 34:02.450
Then take my eyes with you.

34:05.680 --> 34:06.520
Just kidding.

34:17.030 --> 34:17.770
Lu Yan,

34:18.630 --> 34:19.699
would you like to

34:19.730 --> 34:20.550
go with me

34:20.550 --> 34:21.469
to visit Lake Baikal one day?

34:25.830 --> 34:26.400
Lu Yan!

34:26.510 --> 34:28.659
Keep going!

34:28.870 --> 34:30.989
Keep going!

34:31.110 --> 34:34.550
Keep going!

34:34.800 --> 34:37.030
Keep going!

34:37.190 --> 34:39.860
Keep going!

34:39.989 --> 34:41.070
Lu Yan, come on!

34:41.870 --> 34:42.630
Come on!

34:42.949 --> 34:45.310
Keep going!

34:45.429 --> 34:48.090
Keep going!

34:48.150 --> 34:51.190
Keep going!

34:51.270 --> 34:54.070
Keep going!

34:54.150 --> 34:56.550
Lu Yan, come on!

34:56.949 --> 34:57.630
Keep going!

34:57.830 --> 34:58.790
Lu Yan, come on!

34:58.960 --> 35:00.230
Keep going!

35:00.380 --> 35:01.370
Come on, Lu Yan!

35:01.510 --> 35:04.070
Keep going!

35:04.090 --> 35:04.920
Lu Yan.

35:37.070 --> 35:38.180
["Half Love"]

35:44.270 --> 35:47.950
["Half Love"]

35:45.680 --> 35:46.660
Alright, next,

35:46.710 --> 35:48.270
let's give a warm round of applause

35:48.270 --> 35:49.710
as we welcome our publisher

35:49.750 --> 35:50.950
and producer,

35:51.030 --> 35:52.180
Mr. Wen Peng,

35:52.270 --> 35:53.870
along with our production team.

35:53.980 --> 35:54.790
Please come on up.

35:56.150 --> 36:00.550
[Premiere in Ninghai]

35:56.670 --> 35:58.070
Come on, guys.

35:59.100 --> 35:59.990
Alright, welcome.

36:00.190 --> 36:00.950
Welcome, everyone.

36:01.800 --> 36:02.230
Thank you.

36:02.330 --> 36:02.790
Thank you.

36:03.630 --> 36:04.840
Go ahead, Mr. Wen.

36:06.520 --> 36:07.760
Good evening, everyone.

36:08.200 --> 36:10.210
I'm very glad you could come and watch the film.

36:10.790 --> 36:12.500
Actually, we should have the director speak first.

36:12.520 --> 36:13.170
Director, please go ahead.

36:13.190 --> 36:14.010
No.

36:14.470 --> 36:15.900
What I want to say is,

36:16.030 --> 36:18.690
first of all, thank you all for your support.

36:18.990 --> 36:20.090
This film

36:20.120 --> 36:21.420
is actually based on

36:21.550 --> 36:22.570
Mr. Wen's own story.

36:22.600 --> 36:24.490
I think it should be Mr. Wen who shares it.

36:24.590 --> 36:25.550
Don't you all agree?

36:25.570 --> 36:26.950
Yes.

36:30.320 --> 36:31.290
[Premiere in Ninghai]

36:30.380 --> 36:31.390
Yes, Mr. Wen.

36:31.460 --> 36:32.320
And as we saw

36:32.350 --> 36:33.190
just now

36:33.230 --> 36:34.470
in the film,

36:34.540 --> 36:36.430
the male lead has a segment about

36:36.550 --> 36:37.910
the bittersweet memories of his first love.

36:37.960 --> 36:40.270
The kind of regret from a love that couldn't be realized

36:40.300 --> 36:41.620
was very sincere,

36:41.630 --> 36:43.530
especially in the scene where the girl gave him an umbrella.

36:43.630 --> 36:45.000
I believe many of you here

36:45.030 --> 36:45.670
are as curious

36:45.750 --> 36:47.070
as I am,

36:47.230 --> 36:48.570
and I'd like to ask Mr. Wen,

36:48.850 --> 36:49.990
was this scene

36:50.010 --> 36:51.560
based on

36:51.630 --> 36:52.620
your own real experience?

36:54.220 --> 36:54.870
Yes.

36:55.810 --> 36:56.390
Okay.

36:56.420 --> 36:57.980
In the heavy rain,

36:58.070 --> 36:59.220
the girl gave the boy

36:59.260 --> 37:00.230
an umbrella,

37:00.360 --> 37:01.910
and her radiant smile

37:01.930 --> 37:03.110
became something

37:03.150 --> 37:04.270
the boy would remember for a lifetime.

37:04.620 --> 37:06.030
I remember this shot

37:06.050 --> 37:07.460
was handled very beautifully.

37:07.630 --> 37:08.930
So, I'd like to ask Mr. Wen,

37:09.010 --> 37:09.760
is there anything else

37:09.790 --> 37:11.110
you would like to share with us?

37:14.650 --> 37:16.060
In my university days,

37:17.340 --> 37:18.280
there was

37:18.310 --> 37:19.990
once a girl who,

37:21.250 --> 37:22.430
on a rainy day,

37:22.750 --> 37:23.940
unknowingly

37:23.990 --> 37:25.190
appeared in front of me

37:26.000 --> 37:26.930
and gave me warmth.

37:29.360 --> 37:30.970
Is this girl

37:30.990 --> 37:32.990
your life partner now?

37:34.710 --> 37:35.740
Not yet,

37:36.230 --> 37:37.260
but I will work hard for it.

37:38.310 --> 37:38.750
Alright.

37:38.770 --> 37:40.340
Let's wish Mr. Wen the best of luck,

37:40.470 --> 37:41.790
and let's give a round of applause

37:41.790 --> 37:42.630
for the success of the new film,

37:42.900 --> 37:44.940
hoping it achieves even more

37:44.990 --> 37:46.560
in domestic awards.

37:56.560 --> 37:58.130
Would you like to go to the bathroom?

37:58.320 --> 37:59.190
No.

37:59.480 --> 38:00.270
Then wait for me.

38:00.310 --> 38:00.700
Okay.

38:07.080 --> 38:07.750
Yan.

38:07.800 --> 38:09.190
How's the date

38:09.230 --> 38:09.960
with Officer?

38:09.980 --> 38:11.440
You're so busy that you don't even have time to reply to me.

38:11.510 --> 38:12.790
You must be really happy, huh?

38:15.410 --> 38:16.830
We were watching a movie,

38:16.870 --> 38:17.510
okay?

38:17.550 --> 38:18.900
How was I supposed to reply to you?

38:25.170 --> 38:25.990
You're here too.

38:29.480 --> 38:30.570
The movie was really good

38:30.590 --> 38:31.420
It was enjoyable.

38:32.260 --> 38:32.740
Thank you.

38:33.920 --> 38:34.790
If you like it,

38:34.810 --> 38:35.550
please help us

38:35.580 --> 38:36.270
promote the movie to others.

38:36.910 --> 38:37.310
Sure.

38:38.170 --> 38:39.020
I'll go first.

38:45.260 --> 38:45.870
I'm done.

38:46.550 --> 38:47.370
I'm thinking of

38:47.400 --> 38:48.880
saying goodbye to Wen.

38:48.900 --> 38:50.190
-Tell him we're leaving first.
-Sure.

38:51.330 --> 38:53.270
Wen, we're heading out now.

38:53.290 --> 38:54.320
Everything went smoothly today.

38:54.350 --> 38:55.190
Congratulations.

38:57.500 --> 38:58.240
Are you hungry?

38:59.730 --> 39:00.450
I'm not hungry,

39:00.660 --> 39:02.180
but I feel like going for a walk.

39:02.200 --> 39:03.220
Did you drive?

39:04.190 --> 39:04.950
We can walk;

39:04.970 --> 39:06.040
it's not far.

39:06.080 --> 39:06.800
Let's walk.

39:12.340 --> 39:15.610
["Half Love"]

39:22.500 --> 39:23.790
What do you think of

39:23.790 --> 39:24.390
today's movie?

39:25.480 --> 39:27.880
I think it was really good.

39:28.070 --> 39:30.560
It felt like he put a lot of effort into it.

39:31.200 --> 39:32.690
He really did.

39:32.900 --> 39:34.140
All those years ago,

39:34.170 --> 39:35.770
a girl gave him an umbrella,

39:36.350 --> 39:37.110
and he still remembers it,

39:38.070 --> 39:39.280
even turning it into a film.

39:44.080 --> 39:46.100
[Wang Qianqian] [Answer] [Decline]

39:52.250 --> 39:53.430
Is there someone

39:53.940 --> 39:55.340
who you've been thinking about for so many years?

40:03.150 --> 40:03.920
Yes.

40:13.180 --> 40:14.310
Have you been alone

40:15.600 --> 40:17.060
all these years?

40:19.630 --> 40:20.310
What about you?

40:20.350 --> 40:21.160
Me?

40:25.120 --> 40:27.110
I've pretty much been the same,

40:27.410 --> 40:28.380
around the same.

40:28.520 --> 40:30.580
[Wang Qianqian] [Answer] [Decline]

40:31.190 --> 40:31.950
Fine.

40:32.120 --> 40:34.220
You'd dated so many after me?

40:34.710 --> 40:36.550
Things seem to be going well for everyone.

40:36.730 --> 40:38.060
You must've had many suitors too.

40:38.230 --> 40:39.270
Of course.

40:39.270 --> 40:41.160
They'd have to line up from here

40:41.320 --> 40:42.670
to all the way over there.

40:52.320 --> 40:53.310
What are you doing?

40:54.870 --> 40:55.600
Lining up.

41:03.630 --> 41:04.550
As I can see,

41:05.580 --> 41:07.060
there's no one here today.

41:09.120 --> 41:10.490
Can you let me cut in line?

41:22.070 --> 41:23.470
I still have to work tomorrow.

41:23.500 --> 41:24.670
Stop messing around.

41:24.690 --> 41:25.830
I'm going upstairs.

41:29.630 --> 41:30.560
I'm heading back now.

41:34.450 --> 41:35.330
Lu Yan.

41:42.640 --> 41:44.340
Is the CCTV

41:45.060 --> 41:46.490
running low on battery?

41:47.030 --> 41:48.290
Let me check for you.

42:20.270 --> 42:20.820
You...

42:20.860 --> 42:22.700
You can sit down.

42:23.090 --> 42:23.920
Should I put your things here?

42:24.040 --> 42:24.480
Okay.

42:28.450 --> 42:29.380
Why are you standing there?

42:30.350 --> 42:31.820
Do you want something to drink?

42:34.370 --> 42:35.100
What do you have?

42:35.910 --> 42:36.910
Water.

42:38.630 --> 42:39.600
Let me see.

42:44.730 --> 42:45.400
Water.

42:47.090 --> 42:48.480
Your place has a nice view.

42:50.820 --> 42:51.700
Not bad, right?

42:54.660 --> 42:56.080
Whenever

42:57.780 --> 42:59.380
I'm feeling down,

43:00.220 --> 43:02.110
I just stand there and look outside.

43:03.870 --> 43:04.470
Lu Yan,

43:07.630 --> 43:08.820
I want to tell you something.

43:11.270 --> 43:12.600
Actually,

43:14.470 --> 43:15.730
all these years,

43:16.990 --> 43:18.130
other than you,

43:20.400 --> 43:21.700
I've never loved anyone else.

43:24.810 --> 43:25.770
What you just said,

43:25.800 --> 43:27.010
about one, two, three, four, five, six—

43:27.770 --> 43:28.590
weren't they people?

43:29.910 --> 43:31.280
Then what you just said,

43:31.310 --> 43:32.670
about the whole street lining up,

43:33.230 --> 43:34.190
is that true?

43:37.860 --> 43:39.110
All these years,

43:40.360 --> 43:41.710
♫As the city flickers♫

43:42.230 --> 43:43.310
I haven't come back.

43:42.950 --> 43:45.840
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

43:44.230 --> 43:45.680
First, I'm a bit

43:45.960 --> 43:46.830
angry,

43:46.850 --> 43:47.480
because back then,

43:47.120 --> 43:48.410
♫And you, who love to smile♫

43:47.500 --> 43:49.170
you didn't even see me for one last time.

43:49.430 --> 43:51.890
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

43:51.740 --> 43:52.910
Secondly,

43:52.920 --> 43:55.260
♫The humor of time♫

43:53.100 --> 43:54.230
I'm also worried.

43:55.300 --> 43:57.010
I worry that there's someone else by your side.

43:56.750 --> 43:59.200
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

44:00.270 --> 44:06.020
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

44:00.670 --> 44:01.990
I also worry

44:02.450 --> 44:04.250
that you don't want to see me at all.

44:06.970 --> 44:08.250
I'm afraid you've forgotten about me.

44:07.410 --> 44:09.020
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

44:10.130 --> 44:12.990
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

44:13.510 --> 44:14.170
I...

44:14.280 --> 44:15.710
♫The stubborn me♫

44:16.400 --> 44:17.570
I haven't forgotten you.

44:16.940 --> 44:19.640
♫I always think of the far future♫

44:20.430 --> 44:22.490
♫I walk willfully♫

44:21.080 --> 44:21.830
Lu Yan.

44:23.390 --> 44:24.280
It's been eight years,

44:23.870 --> 44:26.790
♫Like a star revolving around♫

44:26.150 --> 44:27.990
and I've thought about you every day.

44:27.430 --> 44:28.740
♫I turn around♫

44:29.910 --> 44:33.400
♫But you're not behind me♫

44:31.170 --> 44:32.480
I miss you a lot too.

44:35.070 --> 44:36.660
♫Losing you♫

44:37.480 --> 44:39.650
♫It's so unreal♫

44:40.850 --> 44:42.280
♫I hurt my love♫

44:42.990 --> 44:43.930
♫But still hope to♫

44:44.680 --> 44:47.380
♫Start anew♫

44:48.580 --> 44:50.580
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

44:51.540 --> 44:53.670
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

44:54.860 --> 44:57.200
♫When you're not here♫

44:57.990 --> 45:01.300
♫Life becomes aimless♫

45:02.160 --> 45:03.840
♫I miss you♫

45:04.920 --> 45:07.070
♫It's so real♫

45:08.160 --> 45:09.700
♫The person I trust♫

45:10.280 --> 45:11.380
♫Insists on separating♫

45:11.900 --> 45:14.820
♫Who can explain?♫

45:15.990 --> 45:17.960
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

45:19.020 --> 45:21.230
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

45:22.060 --> 45:24.700
♫To feel my heartache♫

45:25.470 --> 45:27.050
♫When I no longer have the best♫

45:28.100 --> 45:31.810
♫I miss you missing me♫

46:14.110 --> 46:15.490
[Lu Yan, help me]

46:16.990 --> 46:18.610
[We were watching a movie, okay? How was I supposed to reply to you?]

46:16.990 --> 46:18.610
[Lu Yan, help me]
